        <item>
            <title>Tesla 新款 Model Y 香港登場，內外重新設計科技感更強</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/tesla-model-y-hk-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-model-y-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/tesla-model-y-hk-launch/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 05:35:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Model Y]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290431</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 宣佈在港推出全新 Model Y，率先在啟德 AIRSIDE 地下露天廣場公開亮相右軚版新車，並由即日起在啟德、荃灣及沙田體驗中心展出。後輪驅動版「一換一」計劃後售價為 HK$339,798，最快 2025 年第二季交付。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>這次新推出的「Launch Series」首發限量版，在車尾箱、門檻板及充電中控台等位置加入專屬徽章，並設有投影燈，每次開關車門時，徽章圖案會投影到地面。全輪驅動版本更額外免費配備加速提升功能，0-100 公里加速時間由 4.8 秒縮短至 4.3 秒，駕駛體驗更強勁。這款特別版數量有限，售完即止。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>全新 Model Y 重新設計外觀及內飾，新增「冰川藍」車色，並採用 Cybertruck 及 Cybercab 設計靈感的貫穿式頭燈，車尾燈更為業界首創的間接反射式設計，令車身線條更具科技感。車廂則配備雙層隔音玻璃，全景玻璃車頂能阻隔 7 倍紫外線及熱能，提供更安靜舒適的乘坐體驗。車輪與尾擾流器經過改良，減低空氣阻力，而懸掛系統重新調校後，行駛更平穩順暢。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3></h3><p>長續航版本設有 16 個揚聲器及重低音單元，後輪驅動版本則配備 9 個揚聲器。此外，新車亦配備 8 吋後排觸控螢幕，支援 YouTube、Spotify、Apple Music 及 TIDAL 串流功能，讓後排乘客享受更優質的娛樂體驗。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>全新 Model Y 充電效能提升，使用 V3 或 V4 超級充電器，15 分鐘內可補充 266 公里續航里程，相當於來回荃灣與啟德體驗中心 10 次。Tesla 目前在香港設有 84 個超級充電站（共 445 個超級充電器）及 134 個目的地充電站（共 1,099 個充電器），覆蓋全港 18 區，並維持 99.9% 可用率，確保車主能隨時充電。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my-694x222.png" alt="" width="694" height="222" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my-694x222.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my.png 779w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>來源: tesla 新聞稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
